data.description: Discover a charming 3-bed, 2-bath home on Purcell's north side, with quick access to the highway. Built in 1999, this residence offers modern comfort with a spacious living room, well-equipped kitchen, and a tranquil master bedroom. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility. The backyard is a blank canvas for your ideas. Don't miss out on this motivated seller opportunity. Contact us now to seize this Purcell gem!
